user: I've been thinking about organizing my garage since I got rid of my old sofa bed. Do you have any tips for maximizing storage space and keeping clutter at bay?
assistant: The joys of decluttering and organizing! Congratulations on getting rid of the old sofa bed, and now it's time to tackle the garage! I've got some tips to help you maximize storage space and keep clutter at bay:

